query:
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `documentSections` (
  `id` int AUTO_INCREMENT NOT NULL,
  `documentId` int NOT NULL,
  `parentSectionId` int,
  `sectionType` varchar(64) NOT NULL,
  `title` varchar(512),
  `sequenceNum` int NOT NULL,
  `startOffset` int NOT NULL,
  `endOffset` int NOT NULL,
  `contentPreview` text,
  `metadata` text,
  `createdAt` timestamp NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`),
  KEY `documentSections_documentId_idx` (`documentId`),
  KEY `documentSections_parentId_idx` (`parentSectionId`),
  CONSTRAINT `documentSections_documentId_fk` FOREIGN KEY (`documentId`) REFERENCES `documents` (`id`) ON DELETE CASCADE
);
